Class TokenEx

  • java.lang.Object
    • swp_compiler_ss13.fuc.parser.grammar.TokenEx
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Token
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TokenEx.BoolTokenEx, TokenEx.NumTokenEx, TokenEx.RealTokenEx

    public class TokenEx
extends java.lang.Object
implements Token
    This class wraps a Token and adds a Terminal as specified in the Grammar, as the parser internally needs the association Token -> Terminal.
    Author:
    Gero
